skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: manufactured housing data
des:
Learn how to map the new economy.

The Manufactured Housing Data Assistant is brought to you by one of the world’s top manufactured housing experts. This exclusive data is taken directly from thousands of properties to aid in sales, investment, and maintenance research. Now, for the first time, the power of manufactured housing data is available on your Amazon Echo device. Manufactured Housing Data is specifically engineered to help you grow your portfolio by using a custom algorithm of exclusive, realtime, housing data.

HOW TO USE: 
To use Manufactured Housing Data: 
Say “Alexa, open Manufactured Housing Data” 

Once running, Manufactured Housing Data Assistant will automatically guide you towards exploring exclusive real estate data, until you say 'Alexa, stop'. 

Includes first-ever Fannie Mae realtime data integration by voice.

Some questions you can ask:
"Alexa, ask Manufactured Housing Data to...
* "...start a new sizing guide."
* "...give me Fannie Mae data."
* "...give me the rundown for Class {A} properties in {The Midwest}."
* "...contact Chuck."
* "...give me the rundown on class {B} properties in {Ohio}."
* "...give me a sales quote."
* "...give me ten year treasury note yield."
* "...give me Fannie Mae mortgage lender sentiment."
* "...give me Fannie Mae construction spending."
